 list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Account Representative requirements Interest in accounting, finance, or operations Associate's degree preferred (but not required) Proficiency in Microsoft Word Proficiency in Microsoft Excel Excellent organizational skills Professional communication skills Account Representative related job titles: Account Representative (Part time) Office Account Manager (2+ years experience required) Client Services Representative Vendor Care Representative Account Specialist Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
